# prefix-block-tab-separator-inner

## Input

```
s. {
  a	1
  b 2
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..19
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..19
    WORD_KEY@0..2
      WORD@0..2 "s."
    SPACE@2..3 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{"
    NEWLINE@4..5 "\n"
    SPACE@5..7 "  "
    ENTRY@7..11
      WORD_KEY@7..8
        WORD@7..8 "a"
      ERROR@8..9
        TAB@8..9 "\t"
      INTEGER@9..10
        NUMERAL@9..10 "1"
      NEWLINE@10..11 "\n"
    SPACE@11..13 "  "
    ENTRY@13..17
      WORD_KEY@13..14
        WORD@13..14 "b"
      SPACE@14..15 " "
      INTEGER@15..16
        NUMERAL@15..16 "2"
      NEWLINE@16..17 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@17..18 "}"
    NEWLINE@18..19 "\n"
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "tab separating is not allowed",
        range: 8..8,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..2 "s.",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@3..4 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@7..8 "a",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@9..10 "1",
                    },
                },
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@13..14 "b",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@15..16 "2",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@17..18 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

